                     <h2>NEW TO CUSTOM FLAVORING CONCENTRATES?</h2>
                     <p><strong>You may find the following recipe for tailoring your flavor concentrates useful:</strong><br>Begin with 8 ounces of water, and add 4 to 8 drops of 50% citric acid solution. Taste for proper acidity (orange or apple = more acidic; pear or banana = less acidic). Next, add 4 to 8 drops of our flavor concentrate, and sweeten to taste with Stevia Drops, Sweet Drops (AceK), sugar, or your preferred sweetener. Our flavoring concentrates are significantly more concentrated than our <%= link_to "natural flavor extracts", (Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Natural Flavor Extracts").present? ? seo_url(Spree::Taxon.find_by_name("Natural Flavor Extracts")): '/')  %>.</p>
                     <p>At Nature’s Flavors, our delectable, natural flavor concentrates are made with only natural plant and animal-derived ingredients and never include any artificial ingredients, colorings, or unnecessary added sugar. Enjoy our flavored concentrates the way nature intended.</p>
